<plot>Tico comes home to Miami from Medical school one summer, top of his class; only nobody cares because they're all going nuts. Of course when you start seeing ghosts, have a brother that hates you, a cousin that lands from Cuba with militants after him, your mom and dad at each other's throats, and the family business is about to be taken away by the bank -- no wonder everybody's crazy. Somehow, someway Tico and his family have to discover the truth within them so they can all find their way back to each other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?090287</url></doc>
